011/**
012 * builder for a generic custom object
013 * @param <TValue> The type of the value of this custom object.
014 */
015public class GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> implements Builder<GenericCustomObject<TValue>> {
016
017    private String id;
018
019    private Long version;
020
021    private java.time.ZonedDateTime createdAt;
022
023    private java.time.ZonedDateTime lastModifiedAt;
024
025    @Nullable
026    private com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedBy lastModifiedBy;
027

029    private com.commercetools.api.models.common.CreatedBy createdBy;
030
031    private String container;
032
033    private String key;
034
035    private TValue value;
036
037    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> id(final String id) {
038        this.id = id;
039        return this;
040    }
041
042    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> version(final Long version) {
043        this.version = version;
044        return this;
045    }
046
047    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> createdAt(final java.time.ZonedDateTime createdAt) {
048        this.createdAt = createdAt;
049        return this;
050    }
051
052    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> lastModifiedAt(final java.time.ZonedDateTime lastModifiedAt) {
053        this.lastModifiedAt = lastModifiedAt;
054        return this;
055    }
056
057    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> lastModifiedBy(
058            Function<com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedByBuilder, com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedByBuilder> builder) {
059        this.lastModifiedBy = builder.apply(com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedByBuilder.of()).build();
060        return this;
061    }
062
063    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> lastModifiedBy(
064            @Nullable final com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedBy lastModifiedBy) {
065        this.lastModifiedBy = lastModifiedBy;
066        return this;
067    }
068
069    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> createdBy(
070            Function<com.commercetools.api.models.common.CreatedByBuilder, com.commercetools.api.models.common.CreatedByBuilder> builder) {
071        this.createdBy = builder.apply(com.commercetools.api.models.common.CreatedByBuilder.of()).build();
072        return this;
073    }
074
075    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> createdBy(
076            @Nullable final com.commercetools.api.models.common.CreatedBy createdBy) {
077        this.createdBy = createdBy;
078        return this;
079    }
080
081    public GenericCustomObjectBuilder<TValue> container(final String container) {
082        this.container = container;
083        return this;

087        this.key = key;
088        return this;

093        return this;

098    }

105        return this.createdAt;

109        return this.lastModifiedAt;

111
112    @Nullable
113    public com.commercetools.api.models.common.LastModifiedBy getLastModifiedBy() {
114        return this.lastModifiedBy;
115    }

117    @Nullable

119        return this.createdBy;

133
134    public GenericCustomObject<TValue> build() {
135        Objects.requireNonNull(id, CustomObject.class + ": id is missing");
136        Objects.requireNonNull(version, CustomObject.class + ": version is missing");
137        Objects.requireNonNull(createdAt, CustomObject.class + ": createdAt is missing");
138        Objects.requireNonNull(lastModifiedAt, CustomObject.class + ": lastModifiedAt is missing");
139        Objects.requireNonNull(container, CustomObject.class + ": container is missing");
140        Objects.requireNonNull(key, CustomObject.class + ": key is missing");
141        Objects.requireNonNull(value, CustomObject.class + ": value is missing");
142        return new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>(id, version, createdAt, lastModifiedAt, lastModifiedBy, createdBy,
143            container, key, value);
144    }
145
146    /**
147     * builds CustomObject without checking for non-null required values
148     * @return Custom object
149     */
150    public GenericCustomObject<TValue> buildUnchecked() {
151        return new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>(id, version, createdAt, lastModifiedAt, lastModifiedBy, createdBy,
152            container, key, value);
153    }
154
155    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> of(T value) {
156        GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> builder = new GenericCustomObjectBuilder<>();
157        builder.value = value;
158        return builder;
159    }
160
161    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> of(final GenericCustomObject<T> template) {
162        GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> builder = new GenericCustomObjectBuilder<>();
163        builder.id = template.getId();
164        builder.version = template.getVersion();
165        builder.createdAt = template.getCreatedAt();
166        builder.lastModifiedAt = template.getLastModifiedAt();
167        builder.lastModifiedBy = template.getLastModifiedBy();
168        builder.createdBy = template.getCreatedBy();
169        builder.container = template.getContainer();
170        builder.key = template.getKey();
171        builder.value = template.getValue();
172        return builder;
173    }
